languages.text: "Выходит, ты и сам{mf||а} невысокого мнения о своих сородичах. Но видишь порок совсем не там, где его стоит видеть".
"It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."
languages.original_text: "Выходит, ты и сам{mf||а} невысокого мнения о своих сородичах. Но видишь порок совсем не там, где его стоит видеть".

languages.text: “看来你也并不太看重你的同胞。不过，那些你本该看到的问题，你却并没有看到。”
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: “看来你也并不太看重你的同胞。不过，那些你本该看到的问题，你却并没有看到。”

languages.text: «Entonces, parece que tampoco valoras mucho a tu pueblo. Sin embargo, no ves defectos donde deberías».
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: «Entonces, parece que tampoco valoras mucho a tu pueblo. Sin embargo, no ves defectos donde deberías».

languages.text: 「まるで同族を尊重していないようだ。なのに、目を逸らして欠陥を見落としている」
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: 「まるで同族を尊重していないようだ。なのに、目を逸らして欠陥を見落としている」

languages.text: "Dann haltet Ihr von Euresgleichen wohl auch nicht allzu viel. Dennoch seht Ihr Mängel nicht, wo es erforderlich wäre."
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: "Dann haltet Ihr von Euresgleichen wohl auch nicht allzu viel. Dennoch seht Ihr Mängel nicht, wo es erforderlich wäre."

languages.text: « Il me semble dans ce cas que vous n'ayez pas non plus une très haute opinion de vos congénères. Et pourtant, certains défauts vous échappent. »
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: « Il me semble dans ce cas que vous n'ayez pas non plus une très haute opinion de vos congénères. Et pourtant, certains défauts vous échappent. »

languages.text: "Sözlerinden hısımlarına saygın da olmadığı anlaşılıyor. Yine de mevcut kusurlarını göremiyorsun."
languages.original_text: "It appears, then, that you do not hold your kin in high regard either. Yet you fail to see defects where you should."

traits.locale_text: "Sözlerinden, hısımlarına saygın da olmadığı anlaşılıyor ama yine de mevcut kusurlarını göremiyorsun."
